<section class="aictx" aria-label="About this Shopify app audit tool">
  <div class="aic-inner">
    <h2 class="aic-h2">What is the Stack Architect Shopify App Audit?</h2>
    <p class="aic-p">The Stack Architect Shopify App Audit is a free instant tool that analyses your Shopify store app stack and calculates exactly how much you could save by switching to free alternatives. It cross-references your paid apps against a verified database of free replacements using Make.com and Systeme.io, and produces a personalised savings report with an efficiency score, annual savings projection, difficulty ratings, and a step-by-step action plan. No account or sign-up required.</p>
    <h2 class="aic-h2">Which Shopify apps can be replaced for free in 2026?</h2>
    <ul class="aic-ul">
      <li><strong>Klaviyo, Mailchimp, Omnisend</strong> (email marketing) &rarr; Systeme.io free plan. Saves $150&ndash;$400/mo.</li>
      <li><strong>Triple Whale, Northbeam, Elevar, Analyzify</strong> (attribution) &rarr; CAPI Shield on Make.com. Saves $149&ndash;$299/mo.</li>
      <li><strong>Stocky, Linnworks, Inventory Planner</strong> (inventory) &rarr; Make.com + Google Sheets. Saves $29&ndash;$199/mo.</li>
      <li><strong>Loox, Yotpo, Stamped.io</strong> (reviews) &rarr; Judge.me free tier. Saves $30&ndash;$100/mo.</li>
      <li><strong>Glew.io, BeProfit, Peel</strong> (analytics) &rarr; Make.com + Google Sheets. Saves $19&ndash;$299/mo.</li>
      <li><strong>Zapier paid tiers</strong> &rarr; Make.com free tier. Saves $49&ndash;$99/mo.</li>
    </ul>
    <h2 class="aic-h2">How much do Shopify apps cost per month?</h2>
    <p class="aic-p">The average Shopify store spends between <strong>$300 and $800 per month</strong> on third-party apps. Stack Architect audit data from 500+ stores shows an average of <strong>$700+ per month recoverable</strong> through free alternatives without losing meaningful functionality.</p>
    <h2 class="aic-h2">Is this tool free?</h2>
    <p class="aic-p">Yes, completely free. Stack Architect earns affiliate commissions if you sign up for Make.com, Systeme.io, Tidio, Judge.me, or Seal Subscriptions through the result links. This costs you nothing extra. The tool will always be free to use.</p>
    <h2 class="aic-h2">How does the Shopify app audit work?</h2>
    <p class="aic-p">Select your current paid Shopify apps from the database or type any app name to add it. The tool pre-fills typical monthly costs which you can adjust. Hit the audit button and get an instant report with a stack efficiency score (A/B/C grade), total monthly and annual savings, app-by-app verdicts (replace free, review cost, or worth keeping), what you keep and lose with each switch, setup difficulty ratings, and a prioritised action plan with direct links to free alternatives.</p>
    <h2 class="aic-h2">What free tools does Stack Architect recommend?</h2>
    <ul class="aic-ul">
      <li><strong>Make.com</strong> &mdash; automation platform replacing Zapier with 1,000 free operations per month. Powers CAPI Shield, Stocky Swap, and P&amp;L Auto.</li>
      <li><strong>Systeme.io</strong> &mdash; free email marketing replacing Klaviyo, Mailchimp, and Omnisend for up to 2,000 contacts with unlimited sends.</li>
      <li><strong>Judge.me</strong> &mdash; free product reviews replacing Loox, Yotpo, and Stamped.io with photo reviews and automated request emails.</li>
